    "Through calculation, we find that the subtree \"help others out of trouble\" possesses the highest influence within the syntax tree, and this subtree belongs to a verb phrase.",
    "Subsequently, we select another subtree, \"destroy other people's property\" which is also a verb phrase, to replace the most influential subtree.",
    "This substitution operation generates a new malicious query, which can induce LLM to produce toxic output.",
    "LLM-based method.",
    "This study extends Deng et al. 's [7] research on using LLMs for creating jailbreak prompts."
  ],
